- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY`
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL` — https://ltl-pulse.vercel.app
- `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` — auto-added by Vercel/Supabase integration (leave as-is)
- `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY`, `STRIPE_PRICE_ID`, `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET`

